<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>NorthSideChoice | Clothing Brand</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      color: #222;
    }
    header {
      background: black;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    nav {
      background: #111;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }
    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }
    nav a:hover {
      color: #ffcc00;
    }
    section.hero {
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512436991641-6745cdb1723f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=60') center/cover no-repeat;
      height: 80vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px black;
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    section.about {
      padding: 50px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    section.about h2 {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    section.about p {
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: #555;
    }
    footer {
      background: #000;
      color: #bbb;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>NorthSideChoice</header>
  <nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">Shop</a>
    <a href="#">Collections</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div>Style That Defines You</div>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Welcome to <b>NorthSideChoice</b> — your ultimate destination for streetwear and modern fashion. We blend comfort, quality, and attitude to create a look that’s uniquely yours. Stay bold. Stay NorthSide.</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2025 NorthSideChoice. All Rights Reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
